snippet.title: Check in the Back - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD NOW: https://dipomaster.itch.io/check-in-the-back

Check in the back is a short visual novel where you help convention patrons find their lost belongings.

As the unlucky 20-something manning the lost-and-found office of a large fan convention, help a handful of quirky characters find their stuff! 

If you can supply friendly conversation and quick service, maybe you'll get hired permanently!

Download from Itch.io and extract the folder to run the game!

Music: https://twitter.com/GinaLoughlin

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Consider Supporting me on Patreon or following me on Twitter!
Support: https://www.patreon.com/froggywithfries​
